Package io.helidon.service.configuration.accs

Class ACCSSystem

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.helidon.service.configuration.api.System
      • io.helidon.service.configuration.accs.ACCSSystem

  • public final class ACCSSystem
extends System
    A System implementation that represents the Oracle Application Container Cloud Service system.

    This System is enabled when its environment contains the String key ORA_APP_NAME.

    See Also:
    isEnabled(), System
